  "screens": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "现在把镜头推到盘口最前面。",
        "那里有两个最常见的价格。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "买方愿意出的最高价，",
        "叫 **<term id=\"bid_price\">买价</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "bid_price"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "bid_price"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "在这个价格上愿意买多少，",
        "叫 **<term id=\"bid_size\">买量</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "bid_size"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "bid_size"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "卖方愿意接受的最低价，",
        "叫 **<term id=\"ask_price\">卖价</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "ask_price"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "ask_price"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "在这个价格上愿意卖多少，",
        "叫 **<term id=\"ask_size\">卖量</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "ask_size"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "ask_size"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "先确认方向。",
        "哪个价格通常更高？"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "在正常盘口里，哪一个通常不低于另一个？",
        "options": [
          "卖价不低于买价",
          "买价不低于卖价",
          "两者永远相等"
        ],
        "answer": 0,
        "explanation": "如果卖价低于买价，市场会立刻撮合掉。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "这两者之间的差，",
        "就是 **<term id=\"market_spread\">买卖价差</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "market_spread"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "market_spread"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "价差越小，通常越容易交易。",
        "价差越大，通常流动性越差。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "market_spread"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "但不同标的价格水平差很多。",
        "所以人们还会看 **<term id=\"percentage_spread\">百分比价差</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "percentage_spread"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "percentage_spread"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "它先要用到 **<term id=\"mid_price\">中间价</term>**。",
        "中间价就是买价和卖价的平均。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "mid_price"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "mid_price"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "type": "formula",
      "lines": [
        "把直觉写成公式，就是这样。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "percentage_spread",
        "mid_price"
      ],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "\\text{Percentage Spread}=\\frac{\\text{Ask Price}-\\text{Bid Price}}{\\text{Mid Price}}\\times 100\\% = \\frac{2(\\text{Ask Price}-\\text{Bid Price})}{\\text{Ask Price}+\\text{Bid Price}}\\times 100\\%",
        "spoken": "先用卖价减买价，再除以中间价，最后乘百分之百。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "做个心算。",
        "如果买价 24，卖价 25，价差是多少？"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "先只回答绝对价差。",
        "options": [
          "1",
          "24.5",
          "4.08%"
        ],
        "answer": 0,
        "explanation": "绝对价差先看 25 减 24，结果是 1。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "接下来是下单方式。",
        "最常见的先看三个。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "**<term id=\"market_order\">市价单</term>** 追求先成交。",
        "它尽量按当前最优价格立刻吃单。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "market_order"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "market_order"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "**<term id=\"limit_order\">限价单</term>** 追求价格条件。",
        "它不保证马上成交，但会守住你的价格边界。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "limit_order"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "limit_order"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "**<term id=\"stop_order\">止损单</term>** 先等触发。",
        "一旦碰到 stop price，才会开始执行。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "stop_order"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "stop_order"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "如果你最在意“立刻成交”，",
        "你会先想到哪一种？"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "选一个最贴近“先成交再说”的订单类型。",
        "options": [
          "市价单",
          "限价单",
          "止损单"
        ],
        "answer": 0,
        "explanation": "市价单的第一目标通常是尽快成交，而不是锁死价格。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "但就算下单成功，",
        "也不代表你会拿到想象中的价格。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "这时候会出现 **<term id=\"slippage\">滑点</term>**。",
        "它指的是预期成交价和实际成交价之间的差。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "slippage"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "slippage"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "波动大、订单急、盘口不够厚时，",
        "滑点就更容易冒出来。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "slippage"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "所以你现在该有的感觉不是“下单就结束了”。",
        "而是下单方式本身，也会改变结果。"
      ]
    }
  ],
